Title: [LEO] Elon Dashboard — First Principles Metrics
Priority: urgent
Status: backlog

Description:
## Goal

Dashboard that Elon Musk would approve. No vanity metrics. Only actionable data.

## Key Metrics (Must Have)

### 1\. Velocity

* Tasks completed per hour
* Trend arrow (up/down vs yesterday)
* 7-day sparkline

### 2\. Cost Efficiency

* $/task average
* Trend vs last week

### 3\. Agent Utilization

* % time active (not idle)
* Per agent breakdown
* Who is underutilized?

### 4\. Bottlenecks

* Top blocker right now
* Tasks waiting count

### 5\. ROI

* Value generated estimate
* Total cost
* ROI multiplier

## Design Principles

* Numbers > text
* Trends > snapshots
* Actionable > informational
* Glanceable in 3 seconds

